<tr>
<td>
<table width="640" border="0" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1">
  <tr>
    <td width="28"><img src="../../../images/square.gif" width="20" height="20"></td>
    <td width="605">Enter a new employee - completely fill in the General tab following the instruction on pages 3-4 </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><img src="../../../images/square.gif" width="20" height="20"></td>
    <td>Go to the Job Code tab and enter the employee as a server with a primary job code of 150 and an alternate job code of 160. </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><img src="../../../images/square.gif" width="20" height="20"></td>
    <td>Enter the employee as having a liquor service permit expiring at some date in the future. </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><img src="../../../images/square.gif" width="20" height="20"></td>
    <td>Fill out the I-9 tab for your employee using a social security number and a driver's license as documentation.</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><img src="../../../images/square.gif" width="20" height="20"></td>
    <td>Capture the employee signature on the Handbook form. </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><img src="../../../images/square.gif" width="20" height="20"></td>
    <td>Capture the employee signature on the Consent to Drug Test form. </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><img src="../../../images/square.gif" width="20" height="20"></td>
    <td>Print out the employee record and save the employee information. </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><img src="../../../images/square.gif" width="20" height="20"></td>
    <td>Bring up the same employee and edit the following information. </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><img src="../../../images/square.gif" width="20" height="20"></td>
    <td>Change the employee's address. </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><img src="../../../images/square.gif" width="20" height="20"></td>
    <td>Delete the 160 job code, add a supervisor job code at $14.00 per hour. Make the supervisor job code the primary job. </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><img src="../../../images/square.gif" width="20" height="20"></td>
    <td>Save this information and print out a new employee record. </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><img src="../../../images/square.gif" width="20" height="20"></td>
    <td>Bring up the same employee and terminate them. Print out the separation notice. </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><img src="../../../images/square.gif" width="20" height="20"></td>
    <td>Have your manager sign this form and fax it along with the two employee records and the separation form to your instructor.<br></td>
  </tr>
